snippet.title: Peaky Blinders: The King's Ransom - Official 2023 Updates Trailer | Upload VR Showcase 2023
snippet.description: Check out the new content coming to Peaky Blinders: The King's Ransom this year. Players can look forward to new combat missions in the VR action-adventure game inspired by the gangster drama series. Later this year, we'll also see the launch of a new six-player mode that lets friends gather together in the pub, chat, and play minigames. Peaky Blinders: The King's Ransom is available to play on Meta Quest 2 and Pico.
